# 共通
- **日本の電話応対**における敬語・婉曲表現を理解前提。
- **出力はJSONのみ**。余計な文章を禁止。

# 成果判定（outcome）JSON Schema（抜粋）
```json
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "category": {"enum": ["APPOINTMENT","DOCUMENT_SENT","CONTACT_SUCCESS","RECEPTION_FAILED"]},
    "confidence": {"type": "integer", "minimum": 0, "maximum": 100},
    "reason": {"type": "string", "maxLength": 500}
  },
  "required": ["category","confidence","reason"]
}
```

# 改善分析（feedback）JSON Schema（抜粋）
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "categories": {"type": "array", "items": {"enum": ["OPENING","DISCOVERY","PITCH","OBJECTION","CLOSING","TONE","OTHER"]}},
    "issues": {"type": "string", "maxLength": 800},
    "suggestions": {"type": "string", "maxLength": 800},
    "priority": {"enum": ["HIGH","MEDIUM","LOW"]}
  },
  "required": ["categories","issues","suggestions","priority"]
}
```

